#For Email Setup:

FROM_EMAIL
This is the "From" address on all agent emails. Two options:

Option A (quick, no setup): Use Resend's shared domain:


FROM_EMAIL=onboarding@resend.dev
Works immediately but looks unprofessional. Good for testing.

Option B (recommended): Use your own domain:

In Resend dashboard → "Domains" → "Add Domain"
Enter your domain (e.g. restaurantos.ai or whatever you own)
Resend gives you DNS records to add (TXT + MX)
Add them in your domain registrar (GoDaddy / Namecheap / Cloudflare)
Click Verify in Resend — takes 5–30 min
Then set: FROM_EMAIL=alerts@yourdomain.com